Answer.feedback1: Redundant and way to long for the pay!

Answer.feedback3: Yes...turkers generally look for HITs that pay one dollar for 10 minutes of work.  This should have been a $10 HIT.  I know you said at the beginning of the survey that it could take 1.5 to 2 hours, but most times requester overestimate the time.  Regardless, I did it because I needed the money.  But in the future, you really should offer more for these types of HITs.  Turkers time is worth more than this.  Thank you.
